Title: A Cute Face, and Super Power?! No. 18 vs Vegeta
Writer: Aya Matsui, Hiroshi Toda, Akira Toriyama
Actors: Masako Nozawa, Mayumi Tanaka, Hiromi Tsuru
Plot: One by one, Vegeta and his reluctant allies meet horrific ends at the hands of the unstoppable Androids. A bed-stricken Goku is Earth's only hope, but there's a specially-designed Android waiting to destroy him!
